{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"18203-amigos","title":"Amigos","description":"¡Simo te contará lo que a a los amigos de ella les gustan hacer! ¿A que les gusta hacer tus amigos? ","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nick Cain"],"illustrators":["Catherine Groenewald"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/18203-amigos"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40715/size3/1a157d12838097ede31750fda683a3df.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40715/size6/1a157d12838097ede31750fda683a3df.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40716/size6/3149584520663c60511c70d7047f47e4.jpg","text":"Mi nombre es Simo.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40717/size6/037ff3315ae81f36aa3a9dbb6b9f7640.jpg","text":"Yo tengo cuatro amigos.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40718/size6/254d768ca0a6125a3844a01cdbf079e2.jpg","text":"Sus nombres son Zizo, Lele, Sisa, y Ayanda.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40719/size6/d801bf3e637d255ea19996520c3f73a2.jpg","text":"A mi amiga Zizo le gusta jugar fútbol.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40720/size6/8e2a6f6059d3d0296c230a1b70ea290f.jpg","text":"A mi amiga Lele le gusta nadar.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40721/size6/7da8560df3259d94d64e3afafc86fa29.jpg","text":"A mi amigo Sisa le gusta jugar al escondite.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40722/size6/322ba2c13fd8bd2030c50cf3ac720aaf.jpg","text":"A mi amiga Ayanda le gusta leer.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40723/size6/a798c60db839ca1235cc1f7bf37c8a32.jpg","text":"¿Y yo? A mi me gusta hacer las cosas que a ellos les gustan.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40724/size6/6d11a8950c7a9b1837446845de13dc69.jpg","text":"Yo juego fútbol con Zizo.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40725/size6/f78d60c6f215e14685ff75860b1599d9.jpg","text":"Yo nado con Lele.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40726/size6/c3fda1cd3c99535146e166d49dc59828.jpg","text":"Yo juego al escondite con Sisa.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40727/size6/a66e5df13da9654bb50813a2e53cdddd.jpg","text":"¿Ven, amigo, a ti que te gusta hacer?","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40728/size6/81ffb755ee84db0b7cf91778498a854f.jpg","text":"Ven, juega fútbol con nosotros.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40729/size6/a810fb5727e253449cde3e072df48b2c.jpg","text":"Ven, nada con nosotros.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40730/size6/44ca1f14e4716f4826ec81a039f5cfc0.jpg","text":"Ven, juega al escondite con nosotros.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/40732/size6/630712aeccfa486d79988b6d6291db92.jpg","text":"¡Ven, lee con nosotros!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":103}}